de_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777923","replies":55,"created_ts":1621410425,"created":"15:47:05","title":"租房的楼上，晚上打游戏打到凌晨，甚至通宵，隔音差，听的一清二楚，影响睡觉，各位 v 友怎么解决？","author":"YIFZ","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/YIFZ","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/706e/e93e/433476_mini.png?m=1574226737"},{"id":777897,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1621356596","description":"<p>写代码会让你觉得自己能改变世界，而写字会让你意识到你只能改变自己。</p>\n<p>点击查看部分书法习作，欢迎关注</p>\n<h1>公众号：<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/HHhNUK_JRvZ4sHuYlPXHmg\" rel=\"nofollow\">书法迷</a></h1>\n<p><img alt=\"当爱已成往事\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/8oxc8t8niaF2vtlOvhDgaNRlfIq09wKZSOkQWSbXJRLKzU3icOZ6ehTib9NkcsicZibUL09wNAD6aiacbRsRCCY5kq9Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777897","replies":52,"created_ts":1621405729,"created":"14:28:49","title":"V 站写字最好看的程序员........","author":"Acheron","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Acheron","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a098/f1b2/183140_mini.png?m=1469150523"},{"id":777843,"node":"云计算","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/cloud","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9e1/074f/104_mini.png?m=1621356648","description":"<p>一周前购入了良心云的香港轻量服务器，访问速度确实比福报云快很多。trace route 试了下，在上海是直连的。</p>\n<p>然鹅今天早上发现国内 ping 不通也无法访问。提交工单后，说是出口线路问题就让我重装换 ip 了。</p>\n<p>现在正在备份数据重装中。。。。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Snipaste_2021-05-19_10-25-27.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/19/ltB2DVOYQAxJSGI.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Snipaste_2021-05-19_10-25-36.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/19/AgLR4nDsdvzpXZf.png\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777843","replies":50,"created_ts":1621391792,"created":"10:36:32","title":"刚入手一周的腾讯云香港轻量服务器出了点问题","author":"cloverliang9721","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cloverliang9721","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/aff9/328b/453056_mini.png?m=1621391403"},{"id":777817,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825","description":"<p>据彭博社(Bloomberg)的 Mark Gurman 称，苹果计划最早在今年夏天推出新的 14 英寸和 16 英寸 MacBook Pro 机型，并改进 M1 芯片。据称，新芯片包括一个 10 核 CPU，其具有 8 个高性能内核和 2 个高能效内核，可选择 16 核或 32 核的 GPU 。</p>\n<p>Gurman 说，下一代苹果芯片还将支持高达 64GB 的 RAM，而目前的最大 RAM 为 16GB 。这将与目前基于英特尔的 16 英寸 MacBook Pro 保持一致，后者的 RAM 高达 64GB 。据说，新芯片还支持额外的雷雳端口，以扩展连接。</p>\n<p>正如该爆料者在之前的报告中提到的那样，新款 MacBook Pro 将采用重新设计的外形，并带来更多端口，包括 HDMI 端口、SD 卡插槽和 MagSafe 磁充电电缆。</p>\n<p>在这种配置中，高性能内核将用于处理器密集型任务，而高效内核将用于更多基本需求。目前的 M1 芯片采用 8 核设计，有四个高效内核和四个高性能内核。根据该报告，新的 MacBook Pro 系列还将配备改进的神经引擎，用于处理机器学习任务。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/PFh6lvIyYV_fGglvI9GqFA\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/PFh6lvIyYV_fGglvI9GqFA</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777817","replies":48,"created_ts":1621387730,"created":"09:28:50","title":"消息称苹果 M2 MacBook Pro 最快今年夏天发布，最高 64GB 内存、10 核 CPU 芯片","author":"hahaFck","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hahaFck","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3f76d95c8badee4798edbe90ca41c87a?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":777842,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1583044904","description":"<p>上班开电脑例行点一下检查更新，猛然看到 21H1，现在还在犹豫要不要立刻更新</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777842","replies":42,"created_ts":1621391482,"created":"10:31:22","title":"今天打开电脑，发现 win10 推送了 21H1","author":"jecvay","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jecvay","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5d88/04b8/75586_mini.png?m=1420216041"},{"id":777852,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","description":"不含咖啡因<br />不含糖<br />好喝<br />主要单独水的味道实在不好","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777852","replies":40,"created_ts":1621392767,"created":"10:52:47","title":"万能 v2，求问什么自制饮品不含咖啡因和糖还很好喝？","author":"zeroze","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zeroze","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e149/150f/240831_mini.png?m=1556607801"},{"id":777816,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","description":"<p><img alt=\"1621386866.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/19/vzyRgkOwdpWLuif.png\"/></p>\n<p>昨天在京东的 AMD 官方旗舰店预约抢购 RX6800 XT，产品页面显示有 40 多万人预约。自己写了个脚本在网页端刷也不行，网页直接傻掉不断弹验证码。然后等到输入好几次验证码进去后，发现显卡已经被抢完了……</p>\n<p>在疯狂的挖矿大潮下，是不是只能等发生矿难才可能原价买到好的显卡……</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777816","replies":39,"created_ts":1621387207,"created":"09:20:07","title":"现在想要原价买到好的公版显卡是不是不可能了？","author":"manami","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/manami","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9166/4abd/453453_mini.png?m=1618568087"},{"id":777849,"node":"NAS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882","description":"网络设备条件都 ok，求 mteam 邀请","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777849","replies":35,"created_ts":1621392421,"created":"10:47:01","title":"NAS 7*24，求一个馒头药","author":"damonzhang","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/damonzhang","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/826f1420356f9b7af4d9ce7cd0962609?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":777911,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.oricon.co.jp/news/2193908/?utm_source=Twitter&amp;utm_medium=socia